    • GridMachine

      public GridMachine (String id, String owner, double computationalPower, int coreCount, double loadFactor)
      Constructor which specifies the machine configuration, specifying the id, owner, computational power, core count and load factor.


      Using this constructor the machine number and the energy consumption are both set as default to 0.

      Parameters:
      id - the id
      owner - the owner
      computationalPower - the computational power
      coreCount - the core count
      loadFactor - the load factor
      See Also:
      • for specify the machine number and energy consumption.
